(1, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"2\"]', 1, 'Apple', '7', NULL, 'apple', 'brands/logo/YHlM1sBzt21726052372.png', 'brands/image/qq5x1Ky6.png', 'brands/banner_image/ZDVAjsu5Kl1725768653.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.applegadgetsbd.com/product/iphone-15-pro-max', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-08-22 13:10:05', '2024-11-05 10:16:06'),
(2, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"2\"]', 1, 'Samsung', NULL, NULL, 'samsung', 'brands/logo/0BfavTIDsH1726052364.png', 'brands/image/1BKg9iom.png', 'brands/banner_image/clcVW1oF.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The Samsung Unbox and Discover 2024 event brings a variety of promotional offers across multiple product categories. Home appliances come with eCertificates and substantial savings when purchased as part of a bundle. For computing devices, including monitors, Samsung is offering credits along with extra perks. Discounts are also available on Music Frame purchases and select projectors.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '<p>The Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra redefines the flagship game. It is embodying the epitome of smartphone greatness. Comprising stunning boxy shape, crafted from titanium, exudes sophistication and durability. What makes it truly epic? The AI steals the spotlight, empowering this device with unparalleled capabilities. The camera, a true virtuoso, captures unbelievable pictures, while AI editing takes creativity to new heights. Fueling this powerhouse is a battery that outlasts like 48 hours long. In the realm of smartphones, the Galaxy S24 Ultra reigns supreme, an unrivaled titan that effortlessly claims the title of the best flagship in every aspect.</p>', '<p>Ashadgate<br>Mohammadpur<br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.mobiledokan.com/mobile/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra', NULL, NULL, 'active', '2024-08-22 13:59:07', '2024-09-11 14:59:24'),
(3, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"46\"]', 1, 'Asus', '5', '15 Road No. 15A, Dhanmondi Dhaka 1209', 'asus', 'brands/logo/PWzMAIn8M11726052354.png', 'brands/image/AGmqaDTWZA1725786408.png', 'brands/banner_image/0ymDroM03i1732774747.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/mDUGWdQP9Q1732774747.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/9eux5Mjetr1732774747.jpg', NULL, 'ASUS Innovation and Quality Across a Diverse Range of Technology Products', '<p>ASUS is a leading company renowned for its innovation and commitment to quality. It offers a diverse range of products, including laptops, notebooks, netbooks, motherboards, and graphics cards. This comprehensive overview highlights ASUS\'s wide array of offerings, such as laptops, displays, components, networking solutions, IoT devices, servers, and accessories, underscoring the brand\'s dedication to excellence across multiple technology sectors.</p><ul><li>Displays include monitors, all-in-one PCs, and mini PCs.</li><li>Motherboards and components such as graphics cards and sound cards are available.</li><li>Networking solutions focus on WiFi 6 technology.</li><li>Accessories include headsets and audio products.</li><li>Support services cover product guides, repair status checks, and security advisories.</li></ul>', 'ASUS A Comprehensive Range of Products for Gaming, Business, and Innovation', '<p>ASUS offers a broad selection of products tailored to meet a variety of needs, from laptops designed for gaming, business, and creative work, to displays like monitors and compact desktop solutions. Their product lineup also includes essential components such as motherboards, graphics cards, and sound systems, as well as advanced networking technologies like WiFi 6. Additionally, ASUS provides innovative IoT devices and servers to support both consumer and professional demands.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://computermania.com.bd/product/asus-rog-strix-g18-g814jv-price-in-bd/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-01 13:50:43', '2024-11-28 06:19:07'),
(4, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"4\",\"46\",\"45\"]', 7, 'Biman-Airlines', '5', NULL, 'biman-airlines', 'brands/logo/liSe0vCMrk1726052343.png', 'brands/image/E3c4cM9psV1725780506.png', 'brands/banner_image/fOG42HHL1u1731323088.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/sAEYvj3Pj11731322452.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/2LTQx20rPC1731322452.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Your Journey, Our Priority Soar with the Pride of Bangladesh. Biman at a glance From Takeoff to Landing: A closer look to our operations</p><ul><li>21 Fleet Family</li><li>23 Intl Destination</li><li>7 Domestic Destination</li><li>80 % above On Time Performace</li></ul>', NULL, '<p>Attractive Offers Available  only for a limited time period!</p><p>Biman BANGLADESH AIRLINES<br>Let\'s Fly with Biman SPECIAL<br>OFFER ON THURSDAY FLIGHT<br>Toronto<br>• Discount: 15%<br>• Route: DAC-YYZ-DAC<br>• LIMITED TIME OFFER-BOOK YOUR FLIGHT TODAY<br>• Purchase Period: Up to 30 September 2024<br>• Journey Start: 31 October 2024<br>• Ticket Purchase from Website, Mobile Apps, Biman Sales Counter.<br>Call Center or Travel Agent.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.biman-airlines.com/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-07 15:38:51', '2024-11-11 11:04:48'),
