(18, '[\"1\"]', '[\"2\",\"1\"]', '[\"2\",\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"4\",\"3\",\"24\"]', 22, 'Diamond World', '7', 'Tower of Aakash, 54 Gulshan Avenue, Gulshan -1, Dhaka-1212, Bangladesh', 'diamond-world', 'brands/logo/hMCidE9z741732422010.jpg', 'brands/image/uzZM9zbhMZ1726914238.png', 'brands/banner_image/frLc45ijPr1732943812.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/oUPzGxq1De1732943812.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/tlGzq5Lffj1732943812.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Diamond World offers a wide range of diamond jewellery with competitive pricing, secure payment options, free shipping across Bangladesh, and a strong focus on customer satisfaction.</p><ul><li>Product prices meet expectations</li><li>100% customer satisfaction focus</li><li>Secure payment methods</li><li>Free shipping nationwide</li><li>Diverse shopping categories available</li></ul>', NULL, '<p>Celebrate the spirit of sharadiya with the dazzling \"sharadiya Dhamaka Offer\" and enjoy an incredible 25% discount on exquisite diamond jewellery! This is the perfect time to treat yourself or a loved one to timeless, elegant pieces that radiate brilliance and sophistication. Whether you\'re looking for a stunning necklace, elegant earrings, or a sparkling ring, our collection offers a wide range of designs to suit every occasion. Don\'t miss out on this limited-time offer and make this sharadiya truly unforgettable with a sparkling addition to your jewellery collection!</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Diamond World promises high-quality diamond jewellery at affordable prices, ensuring every customer finds value in their purchase. With a commitment to excellent customer service, all transactions are secured through reliable payment gateways. Free home delivery extends across Bangladesh, enhancing convenience for shoppers. Their comprehensive product range spans various categories, offering something for every taste and occasion.</p>', 'https://www.diamondworldltd.com/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-21 09:46:43', '2024-11-30 05:16:52'),
