(23, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"3\",\"47\"]', 21, 'sailor', '5', '227/A Bir Uttam Mir Shawkat Sarak, Dhaka 1208', 'sailor', 'brands/logo/TbzEUIKsXk1732339130.jpg', 'brands/image/ly4Bt1Xhrn1727515557.png', 'brands/banner_image/QhgdznOfdg1732081337.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/Rr7Pgfcnzg1732090924.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/WhY4w4FLDA1732090924.jpg', NULL, 'Sailor Redefining Lifestyle with Style, Freedom, and Exploration', '<p>Sailor is a distinguished lifestyle brand making waves in the retail fashion industry. With a mission centered around \"Sailing Life,\" the brand embodies a spirit of exploration, freedom, and style. Known for its trend-setting designs and commitment to quality, Sailor caters to individuals who seek a perfect blend of modern fashion and timeless inspiration, making every journey through life more vibrant and stylish.</p>', 'Your One-Stop Online Destination for Fashion and Accessories', '<p>The online store offers a diverse collection of clothing, featuring shirts, trousers, suits, tops, and traditional panjabis. It also includes a range of accessories, bags, ornaments, and footwear to complete any look. Shoppers can enjoy an array of discounts and promotions, making it an ideal destination for high-quality fashion at great value.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.sailor.clothing/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-24 07:06:28', '2024-11-23 05:18:50'),
(24, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"3\",\"47\"]', 5, 'Foodi', '5', 'Foodi HQ 17th Floor Rahman’s Regnum Centre, Bir Uttam Mir Shawkat Sarak, Dhaka 1208', 'foodi', 'brands/logo/mpyb5fibcp1727167910.png', 'brands/image/y2Ct7x1NPb1727167910.png', 'brands/banner_image/Y1BHkgCIt71732770803.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/WQDXshM0YN1732770803.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/53HWUUWRt61732770803.jpg', NULL, 'Fast, Fresh, and Convenient Food Delivery with Foodi Bangladesh', '<p>With Foodi Bangladesh, enjoy fast, fresh, and convenient food delivery right to your doorstep. Discover a wide variety of dishes from your favorite local restaurants, available anytime you crave them. Whether you\'re in the mood for a specific cuisine or want to try something new, Foodi makes it easy to order from the best restaurants and shops nearby. Experience delicious meals delivered quickly and reliably with just a few taps on your device.</p><ul><li>Order dishes from favorite restaurants near you.</li><li>List your restaurant on Foodi to reach millions of new customers.</li><li>Super fast delivery faster than your cravings.</li><li>Live order tracking from restaurant to doorstep.</li><li>Find top restaurants near your selected location.</li></ul>', 'Foodi Fast, Fresh Meals with Real-Time Tracking and Earning Opportunities', '<p>Foodi provides a user-friendly platform that allows you to order tasty meals from local restaurants, with the added benefits of fast delivery and real-time order tracking. Enjoy fresh, delicious dishes from your favorite restaurants while helping them gain more exposure and grow their customer base through strategic partnerships with Foodi. Additionally, Foodi offers flexible delivery opportunities for individuals looking to earn extra income as Foodi Heroes, ensuring that every meal is delivered quickly and efficiently to your doorstep.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://foodibd.com/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-24 08:51:50', '2024-11-28 05: