(25, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"3\",\"47\"]', 21, 'gentlepark', NULL, 'Ahmed Tower (9th Floor), 28 & 30, Kamal Ataturk Avenue, Banani C/A, Dhaka-1213', 'gentlepark', 'brands/logo/Fmm6N3B9a91727177191.png', 'brands/image/dgtnvMGygJ1727177191.png', 'brands/banner_image/Vw8elof6AB1727177191.png', 'brands/middle_banner_left/OhLpPMebqe1727177191.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/wGVPiZlWyZ1727177191.jpg', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d17641.59091317816!2d90.39936617968667!3d23.792933596261832!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3755c70e662a1c1b%3A0x30d41a0bb73fe56e!2sGentle%20Park%20Corporate%20Office!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sbd!4v1727174721263!5m2!1sen!2sbd\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade', NULL, '<p>Gentle Park crafts unique style statements tailored for individuals with refined tastes, combining sophistication and fashion-forward designs. Each piece is created with meticulous attention to quality, ensuring durability and comfort without compromising on style. Despite their premium craftsmanship, Gentle Park remains committed to offering these high-quality garments at affordable prices, making timeless fashion accessible to all.</p>', NULL, '<p>Effortless style meets ultimate comfort with this trendy printed Casual Shirt, perfect for any occasion. Celebrate in style and take advantage of our exclusive offer! Enjoy a flat 30% off on everything, available both online and at our outlets. Don’t miss out on this limited-time sale to refresh your wardrobe!</p>', '<p>Gentle Park Corporate Office</p><p>28, 30 Kemal Ataturk Ave,</p><p>&nbsp;Dhaka 1212</p>', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.gentlepark.com/', NULL, NULL, 'active', '2024-09-24 10:51:15', '2024-09-24 11:26:31'),
(26, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"3\",\"47\"]', 21, 'Rise', '5', 'nobosrista, plot no.-8, a bir uttom mir shaukat sorok, dhaka 1208', 'rise', 'brands/logo/EhfbWrY1Ep1732339183.jpg', 'brands/image/A0HiRQPlBN1727513576.png', 'brands/banner_image/78uROXUPBa1727513576.png', 'brands/middle_banner_left/PqzAlWapdN1727513576.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/WM6m4NjJ451727513576.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>RISE is a trailblazing fashion retailer in Bangladesh, known for seamlessly blending local culture with global fashion trends. By crafting distinctive streetwear, RISE offers a fresh, contemporary style that reflects both cultural heritage and modern influences.</p><ul><li>RISE blends local culture with global fashion trends.</li><li>They specialize in streetwear and offer a diverse range of clothing and accessories.</li><li>🇧🇩 RISE is based in Bangladesh, introducing innovative fashion concepts to the local market.</li></ul>', NULL, '<p>Elevate your everyday wardrobe with RISE\'s men\'s denim pants, now available at an incredible 50% discount! Combining timeless design with superior comfort, these jeans are perfect for any occasion. Don’t miss this opportunity to upgrade your style at a fantastic price!</p><ul><li>Get 50% off on men\'s denim pants from RISE</li><li>Experience timeless style and unbeatable comfort</li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<p>RISE is a trendsetting fashion retailer that seamlessly fuses local culture with global fashion influences. By combining traditional elements with contemporary styles, RISE offers a unique shopping experience that reflects both heritage and modernity. Their collections cater to fashion-conscious individuals seeking bold, innovative designs that bridge cultural and global trends.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.rise-brand.com/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-25 11:27:48', '2024-11-23 05:19:43');
