path, Dhaka</p>', NULL, '<p>Hatim Furniture presents a unique selection of stylish and modern furniture designed to elevate your home. Our collection features a wide array of pieces including sofa sets, beds, dining tables, TV cabinets/units, cupboards, dressing tables, sofa cum beds, study tables, computer desks, and much more. For both home and office, we offer practical storage solutions such as steel and wooden almirahs, wardrobes, filing cabinets, multipurpose shelves, and metal racks. Our office range also includes executive tables suited for all management levels. Explore our full collection online and find the perfect furniture to meet your needs.</p>', 'https://hatimfurniturebd.com/', NULL, NULL, 'active', '2024-09-26 11:31:11', '2024-09-29 08:33:30'),
