(30, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\",\"4\",\"46\",\"3\",\"47\"]', 5, 'Testy treat', '5', 'Hazi Villa, Level-2 Ja/89, Middle Badda, Dhaka- 1212.', 'testy-treat', 'brands/logo/XHqc070bTQ1732339103.jpg', 'brands/image/55IomOyHs31727870254.png', 'brands/banner_image/9UD99r9eI01727870254.png', 'brands/middle_banner_left/kmZWP6uXKS1727870254.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/odyKOZkNfH1727870254.jpg', NULL, NULL, '<p>Tasty Treat is dedicated to spreading joy by offering affordable, high-quality food to people across Bangladesh. Our mission is to make delicious, satisfying meals accessible to everyone, bringing happiness to every bite. Through our commitment to quality and affordability, we strive to create memorable dining experiences for all.</p><ul><li>Tasty Treat started in 2014 with its flagship store in Mohammadpur.</li><li>It has over 200 outlets across Dhaka, Narshingdi, Narayanganj, Cumilla, Sylhet, and Mymensing.</li><li>Known for over 150 items including cakes, pastries, bakery goods, and savory fast foods.</li><li>Partners with Othoba, Foodpanda, Shohoz, Pathao food, HungryNaki for home delivery.</li><li>Strong social media presence with over one million followers on Facebook.</li></ul>', NULL, '<p>10 to15% Off on all products 🎉🧇<br>Offer Validity-September 21 to October 15 🗺️✨<br>For order Call Our Hotline Number 09613-451451</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>We carefully select the finest ingredients to create exquisite and flavorful treats that are as impressive in taste as they are in appearance. Whether you\'re in the mood for something simple or a gourmet delight, our bakery is committed to delivering an exceptional culinary experience with each bite. Every creation reflects our dedication to artistry and passion, ensuring that our products not only satisfy but also leave a lasting impression.</p>', 'https://tastytreatbd.com/', 'Choose Option', NULL, 'active', '2024-09-29 11:37:25', '2024-11-23 05:18:23'),
