(76, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 2, 'Ribana', '7', NULL, 'ribana', 'brands/logo/mkQRC6NACV1731237811.png', 'brands/image/q5Qhnx04SL1731237811.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/vSiTWxi7Rt1731237811.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/g3v8I4kEJu1731237811.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/y1nmW6D76p1731237811.jpg', NULL, 'About', '<p>‘RiBANA Organic’, a growing Bangladeshi brand where they have 100% organic and handmade skin and hair care products like natural soaps and oils. Ribana is benefiting around 500 farmers and rural women as the company collects the organic ingredients from them.</p>', NULL, '<p>‘RiBANA Organic’ is known for its organic skin and hair care products which are made of 100% natural ingredients and have no side effects. Besides, \'\'RiBANA Organic\'\' makes sure that glycerin is not extracted from the soaps which give soothing and moisturizing skin to the consumers, where most companies do not. Moreover, \'\'RiBANA Organic\'\' doesn’t add any color/scent/chemicals with its products. Without harsh chemicals, \'\'RiBANA Organic\'\'’s skin and hair care products are less likely to cause allergic reactions, inflammations, or irritations. If an allergic reaction does occur with the use of organic products, it would most likely be due to a natural ingredient (neem, saffron, milk, etc ), which would be easier to identify.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>\'\'RiBANAOrganic\'\' is very much strict with their quality and Ph. level. They ensure the weight, quality, and well packaging before the final outcome.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Hence, using natural,\'\' RiBANA Organic\'\'’s skin and hair care products, though, ensure that you are getting the real nutritional benefits from its ingredients such as coconut oil, castor oil, neem, goat’s milk, and saffron which are known to soothe, nourish, moisturize and promote smooth skin. Even though the results may be slower for to some people, but the products are gentle on your skin and won’t harm you in the long run.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p>Besides, when you buy\'\'RiBANA Organic\'\' ’s skin and hair care products, you are buying cruelty-free skin and hair care products and also supporting the move towards abolishing animal testing in the industry.<br>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://ribana.com.bd/', 'featured', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-10 11:23:31', '2024-11-23 05:21:35'),
(77, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"3\"]', 7, 'bdtickets', '5', 'Level-5, Plot 2, Bay\'s Park Heights, Road 9 Mirpur Rd, Dhaka 1205', 'bdtickets', 'brands/logo/bKAyvviHvU1731303254.png', 'brands/image/L6nVYNJyXd1731303254.png', 'brands/banner_image/8ZLtm8OLkT1732077344.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/6bWGUlv0SC1732077344.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/FfJAFpRrLP1732077344.jpg', NULL, 'Bdtickets.com Your One-Stop Platform for Convenient Travel and Event Bookings Across Bangladesh', '<p>Bdtickets.com is a top-tier online booking platform that makes it easy to purchase tickets for a wide range of services across Bangladesh. Whether you\'re looking to book seats on popular bus routes, secure tickets for launch services, or reserve your spot at local events, bdtickets.com provides a seamless and convenient experience for travelers and event-goers alike. With user-friendly features and reliable service, it’s the go-to portal for hassle-free bookings.</p>', 'Find the Best Bus Ticket Deals: Easy, Affordable, and Reliable Booking All in One Place!', '<p>Looking for the best deals on bus tickets? Your search ends here! Our platform makes it simple to find the lowest fares and trustworthy bus operators in one convenient spot. Forget the hassle of browsing multiple sites—just select your route, compare prices, and book with ease. Enjoy a seamless, reliable, and budget-friendly booking experience with options you can trust!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://bdtickets.com/', 'featured', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-11 05:34:14', '2024-11-23 05:21:36'),
(78, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"4\",\"3\",\"47\",\"69\"]', 5, 'sultan Dine', '2', '146/G (Old), 59, Green Akshay Plaza, 1st Floor, New Satmasjid Road, Dhaka 1209', 'sultan-dine', 'brands/logo/piIWKqvTd81731386884.png', 'brands/image/4jArhbIOJK1731386884.png', 'brands/banner_image/etTU5q1sD41731386884.png', 'brands/middle_banner_left/Sl2oxgAn131732076930.png', 'brands/middle_banner_right/GzKbwexr7j1732076930.png', NULL, 'Discover the Best Kacchi Biryani in Town!', '<p>If you\'re in Dhaka, you already know Sultan’s Dine is the go-to spot for authentic Kacchi Biryani, loved by locals for its unbeatable flavor and quality. Now, with their new branch opening, it\'s easier than ever to indulge in this iconic dish. Whether you\'re craving a hearty meal or need a quick grocery run, Sultan’s Dine has you covered. Order today and experience the rich, aromatic taste that has made them a favorite across the city!</p>', 'Exceptional Dining Services Tailored for Your Convenience and Delight!', '<p>We are committed to offering four outstanding services designed to elevate your dining experience. Whether you need a quick and convenient meal, our lightning-fast delivery ensures your favorite dishes reach you promptly. For those on the move, our reliable on-time food pick-up keeps your schedule intact without compromising on quality. Prefer to stay and enjoy? Our welcoming dine-in environment provides the perfect setting for memorable meals. Every service is thoughtfully tailored with your satisfaction in mind, guaranteeing a seamless and delightful experience.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://sultansdinebd.com/', 'featured', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-12 04:48:04', '2024-11-23 05:21:36'),
(79, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 2, 'Flormar', '7', 'Adress : 615/9 Bosila Road, Mohammadpur, Dhaka-1207', 'flormar', 'brands/logo/dBlhqEtg3d1732082864.png', 'brands/image/638nT4jWoc1732084927.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/M8neUFK7YK1732082864.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/qxDVd5iUFq1732082864.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/l1x2O3WTk11732082864.jpg', NULL, 'About', '<p>Flormar is a Turkish cosmetics brand that offers a wide range of makeup and beauty products, including lipsticks, eyeshadows, mascaras, blushes, foundations, and more. The brand is known for its high-quality products, stylish packaging, and affordable prices. Flormar has a strong presence in Turkey and other countries in the Middle East, and has also expanded to Europe and other regions.</p>', 'Describtion', '<p>Flormar is a cosmetics brand that sells its products through various channels, including an e-commerce website. If you have a question or concern about an order placed on the Flormar e-commerce site, I recommend reaching out to their customer service for assistance. They should be able to provide information about the availability of products, the status of your order, and any other questions you may have about shopping on their website..</p>', NULL, 'Location', NULL, 'https://flormarbd.com/', 'top', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-14 04:43:00', '2024-11-23 06:26:05'),
(80, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 21, 'Myro', '7', 'dhaka', 'myro', 'brands/logo/pEBcp3pNUg1732634384.jpg', 'brands/image/daDB9EndeN1732634384.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/wVIzxM2lUr1732634384.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/i1nByyWLaL1732634384.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/dMKosnft6O1732634384.jpg', NULL, 'About', '<p>Myro is a footwear brand focused on sustainability, comfort, and design. The company is known for creating eco-friendly shoes made from recycled and natural materials, with a strong emphasis on reducing its environmental footprint. Myro\'s products often feature sleek, modern designs while ensuring durability and support. The brand aims to appeal to consumers who value both style and sustainability, offering shoes that cater to a range of lifestyles and preferences, from casual wear to more active uses. Through its commitment to ethical production and innovative materials, Myro positions itself as a responsible and stylish choice for conscious shoppers.</p>', 'DESCRIPTION', '<p>Myro is a contemporary shoe brand that blends sustainability with style, offering eco-friendly footwear for the modern consumer. The brand focuses on using recycled and renewable materials, creating shoes that are both environmentally conscious and fashionable. Myro’s designs are sleek and versatile, crafted to provide comfort and support while minimizing their environmental impact. Whether you’re looking for everyday sneakers, casual shoes, or active wear, Myro combines innovation with practicality to deliver high-quality footwear that aligns with a sustainable lifestyle. With a commitment to ethical production, Myro appeals to individuals who want to make a positive impact without compromising on style or performance.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://myrobd.com/', 'featured', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-14 06:24:34', '2024-11-26 15:19:44'),
(81, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 21, 'Bay', '7', 'Dhaka', 'bay', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'About', '<p>Bay Emporium Ltd. is a family-oriented footwear retail company founded. Bay offering a diverse range of products for all age groups, from infants to seniors. The company primarily targets middle and upper-middle-income customers in metropolitan and semi-urban areas, with a focus on neo-traditional consumers. With 93 stores across Bangladesh, Bay Emporium Ltd. holds the third position in the country\'s family footwear retail market.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.amarbay.com/', 'top', NULL, 'inactive', '2024-11-17 10:27:25', '2024-11-27 08:22:46'),
(82, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"4\"]', 21, 'HEAD GEAR', '7', 'Kuwaiti Moshjid road, Dhali Bari, Bashundhara, Dhaka-1229', 'head-gear', 'brands/logo/4Mxk6BKaM01732092641.png', 'brands/image/VkbDzK8JUz1732092641.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/mpVFM3uxfc1732092641.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/IVNfNe50po1732092641.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/vYiNu4QOT21732092836.jpg', NULL, 'About', '<p>Head Gear Limited is Bangladesh\'s premier destination for high quality lifestyle products, &nbsp;specialize in offering Top Notch Caps across various segments. From premium baseball caps to trendy trucker caps, we cater to diverse tastes and preferences.</p>', 'Describtion', '<p>The country\'s first cap brand, They lead with innovation and pride ourselves on delivering exceptional craftsmanship and style. Head Gear mission is to redefine the online shopping experience, ensuring convenience and satisfaction for our customers every step of the way.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://headgearbd.com/', 'top', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-20 08:50:41', '2024-11-23 05:21:39'),
(83, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 2, 'SUNDORA BEAUTY', '7', 'Dhaka', 'sundora-beauty', 'brands/logo/BM8rhglYXS1732509041.jpg', 'brands/image/ICpdz5iHtp1732509041.png', 'brands/banner_image/a8sicnq9FT1732509041.png', 'brands/middle_banner_left/CoaFPnnRDr1732509041.png', 'brands/middle_banner_right/tmFWrfgJ8N1732509041.jpg', NULL, 'About', '<h2>SUNDORA BEAUTY IS True Beauty destination for perfumes and cosmetics in Bangladesh</h2>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://sundora.com.bd/', 'top', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-25 04:26:53', '2024-11-25 04:30:41'),
(84, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 16, 'Yellow', '7', 'Dhaka', 'yellow', 'brands/logo/74bINL83jm1732646985.jpg', 'brands/image/8M6wRAiwri1732646985.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/YUUtlfwele1732646985.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/az8RINiUMt1732646985.png', 'brands/middle_banner_right/GdhOXuzaCP1732646985.png', NULL, 'ABOUT', '<p>YELLOW is a popular clothing brand in Bangladesh known for offering stylish, affordable, and high-quality fashion for men, women, and children. It combines global trends with local preferences, providing versatile collections for casual, office, and festive wear. YELLOW is renowned for its customer-centric approach and accessible retail experience.</p>', 'DESCRIPTION', '<p>The vision of <strong>YELLOW</strong> is to become the leading fashion brand in Bangladesh, offering stylish, high-quality, and affordable clothing for all. By blending global fashion trends with local preferences, YELLOW aims to provide versatile, contemporary designs that empower individuals to express themselves confidently while ensuring an exceptional shopping experience for every customer. The brand is also committed to sustainability, ethical practices, and contributing to the growth of the Bangladeshi fashion industry.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.yellowclothing.net/', 'top', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-26 18:49:45', '2024-11-26 18:49:45'),
(85, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 1, 'Oraimo', '5', '278/A,Free School Street,Dhaka', 'oraimo', 'brands/logo/OEzvCFFUGq1732705872.png', 'brands/image/YsIdzUtUhC1732705872.png', 'brands/banner_image/PrgJTvyO7L1732705872.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/Ym4k6Sfb8O1732705872.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/1Gs2rnNCeI1732705872.jpg', NULL, 'Explore More with Oraimo Innovative Smart Accessories for the Adventurous Spirit!', '<p>Keep exploring with oraimo, a brand dedicated to creating innovative and stylish smart accessories for young, adventurous individuals worldwide. Each product is thoughtfully designed to inspire creativity and add excitement to everyday life. Whether you\'re staying connected, enhancing your tech experience, or exploring new possibilities, oraimo empowers you to embrace every moment with style and functionality.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://bd.oraimo.com/', 'featured', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-27 11:11:12', '2024-11-27 11:11:12'),
(86, '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', '[\"1\"]', 'null', 5, 'Burgerology', '7', 'Dhaka', 'burgerology', 'brands/logo/nlKxZF1X751732787040.png', 'brands/image/7ux7YGUlhz1732787040.jpg', 'brands/banner_image/hTVn7q3yof1732964250.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_left/2iXqbnBYFd1732964250.jpg', 'brands/middle_banner_right/hMWKiJVRCg1732964250.jpg', NULL, 'ABOUT', '<p>Burggerology is a unique burger shop that elevates the classic burger experience with high quality ingredients and creative twists. Offering a range of gourmet, plant-based, and exotic options, the shop focuses on flavor innovation, customization, and a fun dining atmosphere, making each burger an exciting culinary adventure.</p>', 'DESCRIPTION', '<p>Burggerology is a vibrant burger shop that combines quality ingredients with innovative flavors. Specializing in gourmet, plant-based, and unique burger options, it offers a customizable experience with fresh toppings, sauces, and patties. The trendy atmosphere and focus on creativity make it a go-to destination for burger enthusiasts.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.burgerologybd.com/', 'top', NULL, 'active', '2024-11-28 09:44:00', '2024-11-30 10:57:30');

